<heading>info - Show system information.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>
<pre>
  info
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Displays system information including current time, runtime uptime,
platform version, Python version, and hostname.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
man
</paragraph>
